-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Mai 06, 2026</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104emn1710839219339.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/emn1710839219339.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/emn1710839219339.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"emn1710839219339\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The list of logical widgets in Uniface.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"emn1710839219339__section_w2217ab1b5b1_w2218ab1b5_w2219ab1\">\n<div class=\"p\">Logical widgets:<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"emn1710839219339__ul_p22_3nk_51c\">\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"taj1665702588022.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/taj1665702588022.html\" title=\"The AttributesOnly DSP widget represents an abstract field to which any HTML element can be bound, making it possible to manipulate its attributes in ProcScript and JavaScript.\">AttributesOnly</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gzs1665702593158.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gzs1665702593158.html\" title=\"Logical widget that represents a Boolean field as check box in a dynamic server page.\">Checkbox</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fux1665702593245.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fux1665702593245.html\" title=\"The CommandButton DSP widget represents a field as a button. The user can click the button to initiate an action.\">CommandButton</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ueq1665702593342.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ueq1665702593342.html\" title=\"The DatePicker DSP widget enables the user to select a date from a date control, such as a calendar.\">DatePicker</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mnf1665702593856.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mnf1665702593856.html\" title=\"Logical widget that represents a field as list that is displayed when the user clicks in the field. It enables the user to select one value from a list of alternative choices.\">DropDownList</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ism1665702594739.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ism1665702594739.html\" title=\"The DspContainer logical widget provides a default mapping to the dspContainer physical widget. It enables you to embed multiple dynamic server pages in a single web page.\">DspContainer</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gri1665702584585.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gri1665702584585.html\" title=\"Default logical widget for entering and displaying data in a field in a DSP. It is rendered as a single-line text input control.\">EditBox</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mkm1719818471195.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mkm1719818471195.html\" title=\"The FlatButton DSP widget represents a field as hyperlink.\">FlatButton</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vgm1719588905334.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vgm1719588905334.html\" title=\"The FlatButton DSP widget represents a field as hyperlink. It is possible to change the value (the text of the link) using the Uniface JavaScript API.\">FlatButton_updatable</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dvp1665702594015.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dvp1665702594015.html\" title=\"Logical widget that presents a field as a permanently open list of possible values, of which one or more can be selected.\">ListBox</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"slu1665702593525.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/slu1665702593525.html\" title=\"Logical widget that represents a Numeric range field as an edit box with a button to adjust the value up or down, in a dynamic server page.\">NumberSpinnerBox</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rwl1665702593435.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rwl1665702593435.html\" title=\"The Password DSP widget masks the value of the field so that the value is not readable.\">Password</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ajt1665702594579.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ajt1665702594579.html\" title=\"The Picture widget displays an image.\">Picture</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vgg1665702594657.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vgg1665702594657.html\" title=\"Logical widget that represents a field as a clickable image.\">PictureButton</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xpv1665702594331.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xpv1665702594331.html\" title=\"The RadioGroup logical DSP widget represents the values of a field as vertical or horizontal group of mutually exclusive radio buttons.\">RadioGroup</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"owj1719682731368.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/owj1719682731368.html\" title=\"The RawHTML DSP widget displays HTML-encoded data in read-only fields as formatted text.\">RawHTML</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hhl1719655537136.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hhl1719655537136.html\" title=\"The RawHTML_updatable DSP widget displays HTML-encoded data in read-only fields as formatted text. Although the field cannot be edited by the user, the field value can be changed at runtime using the Uniface JavaScript API.\">RawHTML_updatable</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"suz1665702592128.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/suz1665702592128.html\" title=\"The StaticText DSP widget represents a field as non-editable text.\">StaticText</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sts1665702592205.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sts1665702592205.html\" title=\"The StaticText_updatable widget represents a field as non-editable text. Although the field cannot be edited by the user, the field value can be changed at runtime using the Uniface JavaScript API.\">StaticText_updatable</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vcf1665702584675.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vcf1665702584675.html\" title=\"The TextArea DSP widget represents a field as a multi-line field containing plain text.\">TextArea</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"znt1709705364213.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/znt1709705364213.html\" title=\"This section provides description for the logical UX widget ux-Button properties.\">ux-Button</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fcc1709705385612.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fcc1709705385612.html\" title=\"This section provides description for the logical UX widget ux-Checkbox properties.\">ux-Checkbox</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"owd1726469066691.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/owd1726469066691.html\" title=\"This section provides description for the logical widget ux-DataGrid properties.\">ux-DataGrid</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"txs1709705504612.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/txs1709705504612.html\" title=\"This section provides description for the logical UX widget ux-DatePicker properties.\">ux-DatePicker</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hzm1777462862844.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hzm1777462862844.html\" title=\"This section provides description for the logical UX widget ux-DateTimePicker properties.\">ux-DateTimePicker</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cch1709705544803.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cch1709705544803.html\" title=\"This section provides description for the logical UX widget ux-EmailField properties.\">ux-EmailField</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"oja1768821871540.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/oja1768821871540.html\" title=\"This section provides description for the logical UX component widget ux-HeaderFooter properties.\">ux-HeaderFooter</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"smv1771221602064.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/smv1771221602064.html\" title=\"This section provides description for the logical UX component and entity widget ux-Layout properties.\">ux-Layout</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hfm1744106512911.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hfm1744106512911.html\" title=\"This section provides description for the logical UX widget ux-ListBox properties.\">ux-ListBox</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"szw1709705424331.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/szw1709705424331.html\" title=\"This section provides description for the logical UX widget ux-NumberField properties.\">ux-NumberField</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kiw1709705558620.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kiw1709705558620.html\" title=\"This section provides description for the logical UX widget ux-PasswordField properties.\">ux-PasswordField</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jrp1709705442365.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrp1709705442365.html\" title=\"This section provides description for the logical UX widget ux-PlainText properties.\">ux-PlainText</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lky1724921121463.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lky1724921121463.html\" title=\"This section provides description for the logical UX widget ux-RadioGroup properties.\">ux-RadioGroup</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dge1709705618953.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dge1709705618953.html\" title=\"This section provides description for the logical UX widget ux-Select properties.\">ux-Select</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"goa1709705635907.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/goa1709705635907.html\" title=\"This section provides description for the logical UX widget ux-Switch properties.\">ux-Switch</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ekm1709715955999.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ekm1709715955999.html\" title=\"This section provides description for the logical UX widget ux-TelField properties.\">ux-TelField</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cdj1709705492399.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cdj1709705492399.html\" title=\"This section provides description for the logical UX widget ux-TextArea properties.\">ux-TextArea</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bxa1709705583218.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bxa1709705583218.html\" title=\"This section provides description for the logical UX widget ux-TextField properties.\">ux-TextField</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ybq1777462965352.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ybq1777462965352.html\" title=\"This section provides description for the logical UX widget ux-TimePicker properties.\">ux-TimePicker</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ysp1709705598086.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ysp1709705598086.html\" title=\"This section provides description for the logical UX widget ux-UrlField properties.\">ux-UrlField</a></li>\n</ul></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_6397648\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_6397648\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Logical Widgets Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Mai 06, 2026 Summarize Uniface 10.4 The list of logical widgets in Uniface. Logical widgets: AttributesOnly Checkbox CommandButton DatePicker DropDownList DspContainer EditBox FlatButton FlatButton_updatable ListBox NumberSpinnerBox Password Picture PictureButton RadioGroup RawHTML RawHTML_updatable StaticText StaticText_updatable TextArea ux-Button ux-Checkbox ux-DataGrid ux-DatePicker ux-DateTimePicker ux-EmailField ux-HeaderFooter ux-Layout ux-ListBox ux-NumberField ux-PasswordField ux-PlainText ux-RadioGroup ux-Select ux-Switch ux-TelField ux-TextArea ux-TextField ux-TimePicker ux-UrlField Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}